      <section eId="sec_48_8_44">
        <num>48-8-44</num>
        <content>
          <p>When used articles are taken in trade or a series of trades as a credit or partial payment on the sale of new and used articles, the tax imposed by this article shall be paid on the value of the new or used articles less the credits for the used articles.</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1951, p. 360, ยง 13; Code 1933, ยง 91A-4517, enacted by Ga. L. 1978, p. 309, ยง 2.)</p>
